Calculating the distances in packages of 25 0000 entries¶

In [ ]:
distance25k = []
counter = 0
for i,j in permutation_list[:25000]:
    try:
        d = nx.shortest_path_length(G, i, j, weight = 'length')
        counter += 1
        print(counter/25000)
        distance25k.append(d)
    except:
        distance25k.append(" ")
        pass

distance50k = []
counter = 0
for i,j in permutation_list[25000:50000]:
    try:
        d = nx.shortest_path_length(G, i, j, weight = 'length')
        counter += 1
        print(counter/25000)
        distance50k.append(d)
    except:
        distance50k.append(" ")
        pass
